Class ProfileIdentityProperties

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.openmetadata.properties.RelationshipProperties
org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.openmetadata.properties.actors.ProfileIdentityProperties
public class ProfileIdentityProperties extends RelationshipProperties
ProfileIdentityProperties describes the properties for the ProfileIdentity relationship between a profile and a user identity.
